        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-extrabold mb-4">
          Powder Junkie
        </h1>
        <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-blue-100">
          A ski resort review web application designed to provide users with comprehensive, real-time insights on mountain conditions and terrain quality.
        </p>
